GAL22V10
AND_Gate

Clock A  B  NC NC NC NC NC NC NC NC GND
NC    NC NC NC NC NC NC NC NC Z  Y  VCC


Y = A * B			; AND gate: Y is high only when both A and B are high
Z = A + B			; OR gate: Z is high when either A or B is high


DESCRIPTION
Simple 2-input AND gate and 2-input OR gate example using a GAL22V10.
Inputs:  A (pin 2), B (pin 3)
Output:  Y (pin 23) - AND combinatorial output
Output:  Z (pin 22) - OR combinatorial output
